OL,5, Amazon is to pay $25 million (#20      
OL,6, million) to settle allegations that it 
OL,7, violated children's privacy rights with
OL,8, its Alexa voice assistant.             
OL,10,FThe company agreed to pay the US       
OL,11,FFederal Trade Commission (FTC) after it
OL,12,Fwas accused of failing to delete Alexa 
OL,13,Frecordings at the request of parents.  
OL,15,FIt was found to have kept hold of      
OL,16,Fsensitive data for years.              
OL,18,FAmazon's doorbell camera unit Ring will
OL,19,Falso pay out after giving employees    
OL,20,Funrestricted access to customers' data.
